trans-unit.source: If the key is present, invokes update with the current value and stores the new value in the map.
trans-unit.target: 如果键存在，则使用当前值调用 update 并将新值存储在映射中。

trans-unit.source: If the key was already in the map, its associated value is changed. Otherwise the key/value pair is added to the map.
trans-unit.target: 如果键已经在地图中,那么它的相关值就会被改变,否则键/值对就会被添加到地图中。否则,键/值对将被添加到地图中。

trans-unit.source: If the library fails to load, the Future will complete with a DeferredLoadException.
trans-unit.target: 如果库加载失败,Future将以一个DeferredLoadException完成。

trans-unit.source: If the link does not exist, or is not a link, the future completes with a FileSystemException.
trans-unit.target: 如果链接不存在,或者不是链接,未来会以FileSystemException完成。

trans-unit.source: If the link does not exist, or is not a link, throws a FileSystemException.
trans-unit.target: 如果链接不存在,或者不是链接,则抛出一个FileSystemException。
